<strong>v3.9  May 3, 2015</strong>

<strong>Bug Fixes</strong>
<ul>
<li>Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Fixed issue #5. When "Hide Non-Eberron Ethnicities" was turned on it was also hiding Warforged body armor and Aassimar's heritage's.</li>
</ul>
<strong>New Features</strong>
<ul>
<li>Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Factions are important in Eberron and when the Eberron source is turned on the "Use Factions" option will also turn on now automatically. This allows for picking a House or Faction from the "Background" tab.</li>
<li>Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Added missing "Valenar" ethnicity and added logic to allow them to treat the Double Scimitar as a martial weapon.</li>
<li>Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Added Gnome's Zilargo ethnicity.</li>
<li>Races of Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Added Feats: Aerenal Beastmaster, Ancestral Guidance, Bladebearer of The Valenar, Boomerang Daze, Boomerang Ricochet, Call of the Undying, Darguun Mauler, Daylight Adaptation, and Dinosaur Hunter.</li>
<li>Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Added Dargunn Ethnicity for Bugbears, Hobgoblins, and Goblins.</li>
<li>Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Added ECS pg39 note for Paladin Lay on Hands used by Warforged race.</li>
<li>Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Added new tab called "Region of Origin". Added many more Regions that can be chosen for any race. Logic setup so that one can only pick a single Ethnicity or a Region of Origin but not both. (Known Issue: If "Inner Sea World" guide is turned on then a Ethnicity is allowed for Humans). NOTE: A new option "Hide Region of Origin Tab" added to hide this new tab if you don't wish to use it.</li>
</ul>
<strong>Data File Authoring</strong>
<ul>
<li>Eberron (ShadowChemosh) - Fix Bonus Feat Artificer tag that was misspelled on the Artificer class.</li>
</ul>


