<strong>v3.4  February 5, 2015</strong>

<strong>Bug Fixes</strong>
<ul>
<li>Some monsters where missing the Eberron Source.</li>
<li>ISWG ethnicities where being hidden when the Eberron Source was turned on. A new Configure Your Hero option was added to allow you to hide non-Eberron ethnicities or not.</li>
<li>The Living Spells creature will now correctly calculate its CR rating based on the rules on page 295 of the ECS book.</li>
<li>Eberron Stock files updated to the lasted HL version so that it will correctly work with the HL Encounter Builder and Realm Works.</li>
</ul>

<strong>New Features</strong>
<ul>
<li>A new Configure Your Hero option "Hide Non-Eberron Ethnicities" was added to allow gamers to decide to hide all non-Eberron ethnicities or not.</li>
</ul>

<strong>Data File Authoring</strong>
<ul>
<li>Eberron.Ethnicity added. This tag must be placed on any Racial Custom Specials that are Ethnicities for Eberron. Without this tag your Ethnicity will be hidden when the new "Hide Non-Eberron Ethnicties" is turned on.</li>
</ul>

